Title: Oomlot Dealt With
Description: $n, you have to get back to the Town-In-A-Box and warn them about the goblin zombies up in the volcano's caldera!
ObjectivesText: Speak with Sassy Hardwrench at the Town-In-A-Box on the Lost Isles.
RewardText: They turned some of our people into zombies? Tell me something I don't know....
